IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. TEX-GRAD-COMPREHENSIVE.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
CONFIGURATION SECTION.
OBJECT-COMPUTER. VULKAN-COMPUTE-SHADER.
INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
FILE-CONTROL.
    SELECT TEX-1D ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-0" ORGANIZATION IS IMAGE-1D.
    SELECT TEX-2D ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-1" ORGANIZATION IS IMAGE-2D.
    SELECT TEX-3D ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-2" ORGANIZATION IS IMAGE-3D.
    SELECT TEX-CUBE ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-3" ORGANIZATION IS IMAGE-CUBE.
    SELECT TEX-1D-ARR ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-4" ORGANIZATION IS IMAGE-1D-ARRAY.
    SELECT TEX-2D-ARR ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-5" ORGANIZATION IS IMAGE-2D-ARRAY.
    SELECT TEX-CUBE-ARR ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-6" ORGANIZATION IS IMAGE-CUBE-ARRAY.
DATA DIVISION.
FILE SECTION.
FD  TEX-1D. 01 R1 PIC V(4).
FD  TEX-2D. 01 R2 PIC V(4).
FD  TEX-3D. 01 R3 PIC V(4).
FD  TEX-CUBE. 01 RC PIC V(4).
FD  TEX-1D-ARR. 01 R1A PIC V(4).
FD  TEX-2D-ARR. 01 R2A PIC V(4).
FD  TEX-CUBE-ARR. 01 RCA PIC V(4).
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  P1 PIC FLOAT. 01 D1X PIC FLOAT. 01 D1Y PIC FLOAT.
01  P2 PIC V(2). 01 D2X PIC V(2). 01 D2Y PIC V(2).
01  P3 PIC V(3). 01 D3X PIC V(3). 01 D3Y PIC V(3).
01  PC PIC V(3). 01 DCX PIC V(3). 01 DCY PIC V(3).
01  P1A PIC V(2). 01 D1AX PIC FLOAT. 01 D1AY PIC FLOAT.
01  P2A PIC V(3). 01 D2AX PIC V(2). 01 D2AY PIC V(2).
01  PCA PIC V(4). 01 DCAX PIC V(3). 01 DCAY PIC V(3).
01  RES PIC V(4).
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MAIN-LOGIC.
        READ TEX-1D AT P1 WITH GRADIENTS (D1X, D1Y) INTO RES.
        READ TEX-2D AT P2 WITH GRADIENTS (D2X, D2Y) INTO RES.
        READ TEX-3D AT P3 WITH GRADIENTS (D3X, D3Y) INTO RES.
        READ TEX-CUBE AT PC WITH GRADIENTS (DCX, DCY) INTO RES.
        READ TEX-1D-ARR AT P1A WITH GRADIENTS (D1AX, D1AY) INTO RES.
        READ TEX-2D-ARR AT P2A WITH GRADIENTS (D2AX, D2AY) INTO RES.
        READ TEX-CUBE-ARR AT PCA WITH GRADIENTS (DCAX, DCAY) INTO RES.
        GOBACK.
